CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 10, 1958, pg. 32, reads: "Opening Day - Members of the Tommy Smith All-Stars, left photo, charged onto Ammon Field last Thursday for the opening game of the Ammon Slow Pitch League.  The All-Stars, defending champions in the 10-game loop, won the opener, beating the Knights of Williams and Luck, 7-3... - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Tommy Smith All-Stars softball team with "Tommy" Smith on right, on opening day of Ammon Slow Pitch League, Ammon Field
